{
  "stem": "162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was in and out because I think he was helping the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in that shelter so long that we ended up not having food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing that we had to eat was bread filled with worms and prunes, and dried up prunes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, I had lice in my head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother used to pick the lice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She used to go like this and pick the lice off my head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day she said, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't stand this anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You and I are going to go to the apartment, and I have to wash your hair.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was so scared because, again, we had to go across the courtyard to the other building.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she took me up there, and she washed my hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I couldn't wait to get back into the shelter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And during that time, I remember they were bringing people in, wounded soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were bloody, and they were-- I mean, some of them were dead, some of them were dying.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother and a lot of the older women were trying to help the nurses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And several times, some people went outside with knives and took-- there were horses, because in that war, there was still a horse brigade.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were horses lying on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And people would go out and cut meat from those dead horses and bring it in, and we would cook the horse meat so that we would have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then the war ended.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my parents and I, I remember going back to the apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
